      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-mate-grey dark:text-mate-white"
      >
        Team Send
      </h3>
      <div
        class="text-mate-muted-dark dark:text-mate-muted-light lg:text-lg text-base py-12 max-w-screen-sm"
      >
        Coordinate emails, SMS, and GroupMe messages effortlessly from a single
